Dmitriy Donskoy - Bomb/Defuse

Counter-Terrorists: An alarm has 
sounded at a top secret submarine
base. We will enter from the south end
of the base and secure the area.

Terrorists: After successfully inflitrating 
a military base, we have been alerted 
to a team of Counter-Terrorists entering from the south. 
A quick decision needs to be made 
plant explosives on the recently refitted 
Dmitriy Donskoy or destroy her cargo in the
underground railway. 

Other Notes: There are 2 bomb targets
in the mission.
